,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T14:20:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3w18G9p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3w18G9p.jpg&h=0a0f8499&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n乜住緊醫院可以走出街食飯嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果係咁醫院係咪都要負返責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解住院病人可以離開醫院範圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T16:11:54.000Z","msg":"住院可以拎home leave㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：早兩個月試過"},{"pid":"0a5b8bb5b2040e7e6d6cfefac0d4ffcb9fb8ff32","tid":1941663,"uid":242050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9595433488d276195f288c4853918475a959896e","tid":1941663,"uid":1159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7e68741ebd4facfcfbf1652b47ef66a21a73775d","tid":1941663,"uid":12510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T15:48:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">病人偷出去食飯唔出奇<br />\n<br />\n可以等到幾個鐘去食壽司朗先出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T16:06:56.000Z","msg":"我屋企人直頭試過同醫院請假返屋企煮飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T17:01:48.000Z","msg":"咁呢個係請假又唔同講法"}],"pinned":{"pid":"3076c3adc4817f44b7fffdbc69bb7774179c3438","tid":1941663,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T02:19:10.000Z","msg":"有無留意到呢幾日有好多傳媒都好似夾埋咁大做「帶着手帶離家出走自私撚」既故仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後林鄭配合聲淚俱下，每次記者會都喺度屌鳩呢啲人自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根本上就係想將大家將個怒氣spin落捉鬼捉自私撚，慢慢淡化林鄭一開始唔封關嘅事，同時支持政府加大監控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乘機推行d監控嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由二月中至三月頭，由支那陸路入境嘅人一直冇需要帶任何手帶，淨係間中喺電話分享location就當隔離左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢啲嘢又冇人講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下次見到有「哇有個手帶人又去XXX食嘢」呢一類post，嘗試下唔好講「 仆你個街又係呢啲自私撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n試吓講「呢啲自私撚固然唔應該出街，但最仆街嘅都係林鄭一開始唔支那封關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />害死全香港人」"}}